---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Read how Unleft collects, uses, stores, and protects contact form, analytics, and cookie data for visitors to unleft.space."
  keywords="Unleft privacy policy, data protection, analytics privacy, cookie data, contact form privacy"
  imageAlt="Unleft privacy policy page preview"
  ogType="article"
>
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 px-4">
      <Badge className="mb-6 bg-accent-primary/10 text-accent-glow border-none mx-auto w-fit font-gupter">Legal & Safety</Badge>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8 tracking-tighter">
        Privacy <span class="text-accent-primary">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Transparency is at our core. Here is how we handle your data with precision and care.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-mono text-accent-glow uppercase tracking-widest">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-accent-primary/5 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-[#2D2D44] bg-[#0A0A0F]/60 p-8 md:p-12 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-2xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:gap-16 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">We collect information you provide directly when using our contact form: your name, email address, company name (optional), and message content. We do not collect sensitive personal data.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 list-disc pl-5 marker:text-accent-primary/60 text-base/loose">
              <li>To respond to your inquiries and project requests</li>
              <li>To improve our services</li>
              <li>To send follow-up communications (only if consent is given)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">Contact form submissions are routed through <strong class="text-text-primary font-medium">FormSubmit.co</strong>, a third-party form processing service, and delivered to our inbox. We do not maintain a database of user submissions beyond email records. All data transmission is encrypted via TLS. FormSubmit's handling of your data is governed by <a href="https://formsubmit.co/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-glow hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors underline underline-offset-4 decoration-accent-primary/30">FormSubmit's Privacy Policy</a>. Data is processed in accordance with Bangladesh's Personal Data Protection Ordinance 2025.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4 list-disc pl-5 marker:text-accent-primary/60 text-base/loose">
              <li><strong class="text-text-primary font-medium">FormSubmit.co</strong> — Contact form processing and email delivery. Spam protection is provided natively by FormSubmit.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-text-primary font-medium">Google Analytics</strong> — We use GA4 for anonymized usage insights to improve our website. IP anonymization is active and data retention is set to 2 months.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-text-primary font-medium">Self-hosted fonts via fontsource</strong> — All typography is loaded from our own server; no requests are made to Google Fonts or any external font CDN.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">5. Cookies</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">We use essential cookies for site functionality. Analytics cookies are used to understand website traffic. See our <a href="/legal/cookies" class="text-accent-glow hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors underline underline-offset-4 decoration-accent-primary/30">Cookie Policy</a> for details.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">6. Your Rights</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">You have the right to request access, correction, or deletion of any personal data we hold. Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@unleft.space" class="text-accent-glow hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors underline underline-offset-4 decoration-accent-primary/30">hello@unleft.space</a>.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">7. Contact</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">For privacy-related inquiries: <a href="mailto:hello@unleft.space" class="text-accent-glow hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors underline underline-offset-4 decoration-accent-primary/30">hello@unleft.space</a></p>
            <p class="text-base/loose">Location: Dhaka, Bangladesh</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
